<ModOps>
    
    <!-- Problems: -->
    <!-- The category of a Propaganda article is automatically made based on the first ArticleEffect within ArticleEffects -->
     <!-- (of if ArticleEffects is empty then the base ArticleEffect) -->
    <!-- This is of course massive bullshit.. -->
    <!-- These ArticleEffect are Enums, so limited. In NewspaperScene is then defined what text is displayed for this category/this effect -->
    
    <!-- And every category can only display 3 articles, one per ArticleStrength (if multiple , they overwrite each other) -->
    
    <!-- Although there is an ArticleEffect Enum for Anarchy, it does nothing and has not effect ingame. -->
    <!-- Instead the game uses IsAnarchyArticle=1 to mark them regardless of their Effects as Anarchy Category. -->
    <!-- The problem is, that this IsAnarchyArticle=1 has a hidden DLC Lock, artciles with this do not work in a game -->
     <!-- from someone not owning the DLC (if DLC is owend, it works, even without Mercier in game)     -->
    
    <!-- einzige Lösung ist also als ersten Effect Anarchy einzutragen,  -->
     <!-- die Scene zu füllen, -->
      <!-- und dass auf der Karte dann nur einer der effekte angezeigt wird (weil insg. nur 2 angezeigt werden) -->
       <!-- aber beim drüber hovern werden dann alle angezeigt. -->
    
    
    <!-- allow anarchy newspaper article propganda buffs even without Mercier in game -->
    <!-- they unlock with 300 workers -->
    
    <!-- Add new Assets for them -->
    <!-- IsAnarchyArticle also blocks it if no DLC is owned, but I think it has no downside to remove it -->
